high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the front of the toilet.
Pick up the left-most spray bottle on the back of the toilet.
Look down and locate the gray bin to the right of the toilet.
Place the spray bottle in the bin.
Move slightly to your right to stand in front of the gray bin.
Pick up the spray bottle on the back of the toilet.
Move to slightly to your left to stand in front of the toilet.
Place the spray bottle in the gray bin to the right of the first spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles from the back of the toilet to the gray bin

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the end of the room, then turn to the toilet on your right.
Pick up the blue spray bottle on the left of the back of the toilet.
Step over to the front of the garbage can on the right side of the toilet.
Place the blue spray bottle in the garbage can.
Move closer to the back of the toilet.
Pick up the other blue spray bottle on the back of the toilet.
Step away from the toilet to your left.
Place the other blue spray bottle in the garbage can on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in the garbage can.

high_descs: Turn right and face the toilet to your right.
Take the spray bottle from the toilet in front of you.
Face the can near the toilet in front of you.
Place the spray bottle in the can in front of you.
Turn right and face the toilet on your left.
Take the second spray bottle from the toilet in front of you.
Turn around in a circle and face the can in front of you.
Place the spray bottle in the can on the right of the toilet in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place the spray bottle in the can on the right of the toilet.
